{"tid":1614951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位前線做嘢前顧及一下文宣組感受","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:51.000Z","uid":57911,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"86649eae751f7525e0051e9d8800162b30304d29","tid":1614951,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"長話短說<br />\n有啲嘢做完出嚟大家都睇得好爽<br />\n但係事後要兜係比想像中難<br />\n與其幫前線兜我會想擺返條戰線落國際文宣<br />\n係核彈都唔割<br />\n但亦都唔想太多嘢要顧<br />\n始終人手有限仲要同返自己人解釋係好吃力<br />\n希望前線管好自己條底線<br />\n你哋做啲咩都係交俾你哋自己決定<br />\n做法不完美，但可接受，要改善"},{"pid":"e0699224232d6a0cf9b40a118828abe78a9025b0","tid":1614951,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"806ff697c476e4545ff8dfd8f64f2c6ee9aa536d","tid":1614951,"uid":155137,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"真正嘅文宣係能夠支持勇武<br />\n而唔係要勇敢自廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61ae5f2f9fe5e694edc6f38b6e1d93031484fcf","tid":1614951,"uid":69756,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"真正嘅武勇係做野前深思熟慮<br />\n知道咩野應該做咩野唔應該做<br />\n為訴求為外界認同而行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe25c5772a0eb3afc46e60a9ebb5074d60c1dc5","tid":1614951,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c61ae5f2f9fe5e694edc6f38b6e1d93031484fcf","tid":1614951,"uid":69756,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"真正嘅武勇係做野前深思熟慮<br />\n知道咩野應該做咩野唔應該做<br />\n為訴求為外界認同而行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ccdada2d54da2f1b640fc30dbdb195a4c9f2dc","tid":1614951,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac